node.text:
This home was too beautiful not to share!

Interior designer @suzannewinstonandassociates offers an inside look at the 2020 Inspiration Home in Fairhope’s North Hills community. 

The home was built by @reehlco, designed by @mccowndesign and @hannahstefanek served as the design liaison. 

🎥: @mondainifilms #mobilebaymagazine #mbinspirationhome #fairhopealabama

✨G E T ✨I N S P I R E D✨ We are so excited to announce the 2021 Inspiration Home opening this winter! 

This stunning home is located on the Bluff in downtown Fairhope, nestled into a historic enclave overlooking Mobile Bay.

We are thrilled to have Rebecca Bryant (@watershedgreen) and SCC Group on board to create our first ever green Inspiration Home 🌿

Click our bio link for more information about this year’s home and watch our stories for progress pics and updates 🛠
